Horrifying images of a baby elephant tied to a pole and forced to perform tricks has sparked a push to have it freed , just weeks after one of the endangered animals was ridden by drunken tourists around a swimming pool .
The campaign was kicked off by Jaime Singleton , who saw the baby elephant , Nadia tied to pole outside a restaurant at Marina Phuket Resort in December last year .
The change.org petition has received 50,627 signatures since it was launched a month ago .
